Titolo: The Metronomicon: Slay the Dance Floor

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: The Metronomicon: Slay the Dance Floor is a rhythm game developed by American indie studio Puuba. The Metronomicon: Slay the Dance Floor was originally released on September 29, 2016, for Microsoft Windows and macOS, under the name "The Metronomicon". On August 29, 2017, Puuba added new content and released the game for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on August 30, 2017 under the expanded name "The Metronomicon: Slay the Dance Floor".